					<section>
						<h2>Form meets function</h2>
						<ul style="float: left; width: 45%">
							<li><b>Objective</b> link form to function. <span style="float: right"><cite>Gero '90, Qian '96</cite></span></li>
							<li class="fragment" data-fragment-index="100"><b>Problem</b><br />more than one possible interpretation. <span style="float: right"><cite>Roy '02</cite></span></li>
							<li class="fragment zoom-out" data-fragment-index="200"><em><b>Need to incorporate context.</b></em></li>
						</ul>
						<table class="hanoi" style="float: right; width: 45%;"><tr>
							<td>
								<img src="images/fi_threaded_link.png" width="100px"  />
